<!DOCTYPE html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Kanit" rel="stylesheet">

    <title>Welcome To Bay Face Network Monitoring</title>

    <style>
        body,
        html {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Kanit', sans-serif;
            background: rgba(11, 11, 20, 0.51);
            background: linear-gradient(225deg, rgba(11, 11, 20, 0.51) 0%, #0b0b14 100%);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #eeeeee;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: lighter;
            color: #7e7e7e;
        }

        span a {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #cccccc;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: all 0.4s ease-in-out;
        }
        span a:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .floating {
            width: 500px;
            animation-name: floating;
            animation-duration: 3s;
            animation-iteration-count: infinite;
            animation-timing-function: ease-in-out;
            margin-left: 30px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        @keyframes floating {
            from { transform: translate(0,  0px); }
            65%  { transform: translate(0, 15px); }
            to   { transform: translate(0, -0px); }
        }

        .content {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 700px;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            text-align: center;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">
    <div>
        <img class="floating" src="../img/server.png"/>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h1>THE BAY FACE DISPLAY SYSTEM FOR MONITORING THE NETWORK DEVICES
        </h1>
        <p>BY: Mr.Yosapat Thamarongrak</p>
    </div>
</div>

</body>

</html>